description:
"WHYYYYYYY" Supercut from one of the most infamous songs in all of Andrew Lloyd Webberdom - Gethsemene, from #JCS, Jesus Christ Superstar. Why? because he is risen (in that he can hit that high note [some of the time]). Yes, I know there was already a JCS supercut on YouTube - it was time for a new one.

Jesus is coming out of his cave, and he's been doing just fine. 

Pre-order my book - https://t.co/YB0oyrlAUX?amp=1
Twitter - @thelindsayellis
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/lindsayellis
